li></ol><p><strong><br></strong></p><ol start="10"><li style="list-style-type: none;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: none;"><ol start="4"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;"><p dir="ltr" role="presentation">We may further use the collected information to analyse the use of the Website or the Services, and the people visiting and using the Website, for the purpose of improving the features of the Website. We may use Your information to analyse Your use of the Website for providing You customized content, [advertisements] and features. Information provided by You helps us in responding to Your customer service requests and support needs more efficiently.</p></li></ol></li></ol><p><strong><br></strong></p><ol start="10"><li style="list-style-type: none;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: none;"><ol start="5"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;"><p dir="ltr" role="presentation">We may use information in the aggregate to understand how users, as a group are using the Website or the Services</p></li></ol></li></ol><p><strong><br></strong></p><ol start="10"><li style="list-style-type: none;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: none;"><ol start="6"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;"><p dir="ltr" role="presentation">We may use your personal information to prevent or take action against activities that are, or may be, in breach of any policy of Onsyde including the Terms and Conditions and any applicable laws.</p></li></ol></li></ol><p><strong><br></strong></p><ol start="10"><li style="list-style-type: none;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: none;"><ol start="7"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;" data-mce-style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;"><p dir="ltr" role="presentation">We may use Your non-personal information like information regarding third-party apps, including withou